fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.themes

Interface IStylePackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IStylePackage>, IPackage, Iterable<IStyleSheet>

    public interface IStylePackage
extends IPackage, Comparable<IStylePackage>, Iterable<IStyleSheet>
    Represents a package of style sheets that can be applied to a specific template package.

    Style packages can be used directly in for-each constructs, to iterate over style sheets.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be safe for concurrent access.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
